data.description: Welcome to the market 2935 Mary Dr of Forrest City, AR.  This house sits on a .78+/- acre corner lot with pond access in a well established neighborhood. It boast 2 large living areas each with its own wood burning fire place.  The kitchen has new custom backsplash along with newly installed dishwasher and countertop stove.  The master bathroom has a large new custom shower and double vanity.  There is new paint and ceiling fans throughout. Newly installed outside HVAC unit as well.  If you take the steps down from the drive way you will arrive at a small dock on the pond where you can fish or enjoy your evenings.  Call today to make this house your home.
